{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 16,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 591.53,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.762,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now it came to pass that after I, Nephi, had made an end",
      "verse": "16:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.942,
      "end": 7.146,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of speaking to my brethren, behold they said unto me:",
      "verse": "16:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 7.326,
      "end": 9.741,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thou hast declared unto us hard things,",
      "verse": "16:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 9.921,
      "end": 12.057,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "more than we are able to bear.",
      "verse": "16:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 12.737,
      "end": 15.105,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I said unto them",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 15.285,
      "end": 19.14,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I knew that I had spoken hard things against the wicked,",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 19.32,
      "end": 20.853,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the truth;",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 21.033,
      "end": 23.541,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the righteous have I justified,",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 23.721,
      "end": 27.39,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and testified that they should be lifted up at the last day;",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 27.57,
      "end": 31.192,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, the guilty taketh the truth to be hard,",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 31.372,
      "end": 34.019,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for it cutteth them to the very center.",
      "verse": "16:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 34.699,
      "end": 37.439,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now my brethren, if ye were righteous",
      "verse": "16:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 37.619,
      "end": 40.034,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and were willing to hearken to the truth,",
      "verse": "16:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 40.214,
      "end": 42.211,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and give heed unto it,",
      "verse": "16:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 42.391,
      "end": 45.363,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye might walk uprightly before God,",
      "verse": "16:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 45.543,
      "end": 47.261,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then ye would not murmur",
      "verse": "16:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 47.441,
      "end": 49.159,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the truth, and say:",
      "verse": "16:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 49.339,
      "end": 51.661,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thou speakest hard things against us.",
      "verse": "16:3",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 52.341,
      "end": 57.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, did exhort my brethren, with all diligence,",
      "verse": "16:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 57.629,
      "end": 59.812,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to keep the commandments of the Lord.",
      "verse": "16:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 60.492,
      "end": 64.486,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they did humble themselves before the Lord;",
      "verse": "16:5",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 64.666,
      "end": 68.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that I had joy and great hopes of them,",
      "verse": "16:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 68.329,
      "end": 71.301,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they would walk in the paths of righteousness.",
      "verse": "16:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 71.981,
      "end": 76.207,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now, all these things were said and done as my father dwelt in a tent",
      "verse": "16:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 76.387,
      "end": 78.802,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the valley which he called Lemuel.",
      "verse": "16:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 79.482,
      "end": 81.897,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi,",
      "verse": "16:7",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 82.077,
      "end": 84.956,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "took one of the daughters of Ishmael to wife;",
      "verse": "16:7",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 85.136,
      "end": 89.455,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also, my brethren took of the daughters of Ishmael to wife;",
      "verse": "16:7",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 89.635,
      "end": 93.49,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also Zoram took the eldest daughter of Ishmael to wife.",
      "verse": "16:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 94.17,
      "end": 96.353,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus my father had fulfilled",
      "verse": "16:8",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 96.533,
      "end": 100.062,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "all the commandments of the Lord which had been given unto him.",
      "verse": "16:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 100.242,
      "end": 103.771,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also, I, Nephi, had been blessed of the Lord exceedingly.",
      "verse": "16:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 104.451,
      "end": 109.792,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the voice of the Lord spake unto my father by night,",
      "verse": "16:9",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 109.972,
      "end": 112.387,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and commanded him that on the morrow",
      "verse": "16:9",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 112.567,
      "end": 115.864,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he should take his journey into the wilderness.",
      "verse": "16:9",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 116.544,
      "end": 120.166,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that as my father arose in the morning,",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 120.346,
      "end": 122.575,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and went forth to the tent door,",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 122.755,
      "end": 124.566,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to his great astonishment",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 124.746,
      "end": 129.111,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he beheld upon the ground a round ball of curious workmanship;",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 129.291,
      "end": 131.102,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it was of fine brass.",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 131.282,
      "end": 133.418,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And within the ball were two spindles;",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 133.598,
      "end": 135.548,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the one pointed the way",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 135.728,
      "end": 138.004,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whither we should go into the wilderness.",
      "verse": "16:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 138.684,
      "end": 141.656,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we did gather together",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 141.836,
      "end": 145.226,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whatsoever things we should carry into the wilderness,",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 145.406,
      "end": 149.586,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all the remainder of our provisions which the Lord had given unto us;",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 149.766,
      "end": 152.46,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we did take seed of every kind",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 152.64,
      "end": 155.101,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we might carry into the wilderness.",
      "verse": "16:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 155.781,
      "end": 158.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we did take our tents",
      "verse": "16:12",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 158.84,
      "end": 162.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and depart into the wilderness, across the river Laman.",
      "verse": "16:12",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 162.864,
      "end": 167.229,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we traveled for the space of four days,",
      "verse": "16:13",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 167.409,
      "end": 170.01,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nearly a south-southeast direction,",
      "verse": "16:13",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 170.19,
      "end": 172.605,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we did pitch our tents again;",
      "verse": "16:13",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 172.785,
      "end": 175.85,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we did call the name of the place Shazer.",
      "verse": "16:13",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 176.53,
      "end": 180.942,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we did take our bows and our arrows,",
      "verse": "16:14",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 181.122,
      "end": 185.255,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and go forth into the wilderness to slay food for our families;",
      "verse": "16:14",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 185.435,
      "end": 188.175,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after we had slain food for our families",
      "verse": "16:14",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 188.355,
      "end": 190.816,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we did return again to our families",
      "verse": "16:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 190.996,
      "end": 193.55,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the wilderness, to the place of Shazer.",
      "verse": "16:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 193.73,
      "end": 196.749,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we did go forth again in the wilderness,",
      "verse": "16:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 196.929,
      "end": 198.833,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "following the same direction,",
      "verse": "16:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 199.013,
      "end": 202.496,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "keeping in the most fertile parts of the wilderness,",
      "verse": "16:14",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 202.676,
      "end": 205.37,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were in the borders near the Red Sea.",
      "verse": "16:14",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 206.05,
      "end": 210.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we did travel for the space of many days,",
      "verse": "16:15",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 210.456,
      "end": 212.035,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "slaying food by the way,",
      "verse": "16:15",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 212.215,
      "end": 214.63,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with our bows and our arrows",
      "verse": "16:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 214.81,
      "end": 216.993,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and our stones and our slings.",
      "verse": "16:15",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 217.673,
      "end": 220.645,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we did follow the directions of the ball,",
      "verse": "16:16",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 220.825,
      "end": 224.076,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which led us in the more fertile parts of the wilderness.",
      "verse": "16:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 224.756,
      "end": 228.053,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after we had traveled for the space of many days,",
      "verse": "16:17",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 228.233,
      "end": 231.391,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we did pitch our tents for the space of a time,",
      "verse": "16:17",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 231.571,
      "end": 234.172,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we might again rest ourselves",
      "verse": "16:17",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 234.352,
      "end": 237.092,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and obtain food for our families.",
      "verse": "16:17",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 237.772,
      "end": 242.091,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that as I, Nephi, went forth to slay food,",
      "verse": "16:18",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 242.271,
      "end": 244.175,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, I did break my bow,",
      "verse": "16:18",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 244.355,
      "end": 246.491,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was made of fine steel;",
      "verse": "16:18",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 246.671,
      "end": 248.575,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after I did break my bow,",
      "verse": "16:18",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 248.755,
      "end": 250.984,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, my brethren were angry with me",
      "verse": "16:18",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 251.164,
      "end": 253.254,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the loss of my bow,",
      "verse": "16:18",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 253.434,
      "end": 255.292,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for we did obtain no food.",
      "verse": "16:18",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 255.972,
      "end": 260.616,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we did return without food to our families,",
      "verse": "16:19",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 260.796,
      "end": 264.0,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and being much fatigued, because of their journeying,",
      "verse": "16:19",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 264.18,
      "end": 266.874,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they did suffer much for the want of food.",
      "verse": "16:19",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 267.554,
      "end": 272.384,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that Laman and Lemuel and the sons of Ishmael",
      "verse": "16:20",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 272.564,
      "end": 274.886,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did begin to murmur exceedingly,",
      "verse": "16:20",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 275.066,
      "end": 278.781,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of their sufferings and afflictions in the wilderness;",
      "verse": "16:20",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 278.961,
      "end": 282.63,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my father began to murmur against the Lord his God;",
      "verse": "16:20",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 282.81,
      "end": 285.596,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and they were all exceedingly sorrowful,",
      "verse": "16:20",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 285.776,
      "end": 288.33,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even that they did murmur against the Lord.",
      "verse": "16:20",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 289.01,
      "end": 291.518,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now it came to pass that I, Nephi,",
      "verse": "16:21",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 291.698,
      "end": 296.435,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having been afflicted with my brethren because of the loss of my bow,",
      "verse": "16:21",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 296.615,
      "end": 298.937,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their bows having lost their springs,",
      "verse": "16:21",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 299.117,
      "end": 301.439,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it began to be exceedingly difficult,",
      "verse": "16:21",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 301.619,
      "end": 304.266,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, insomuch that we could obtain no food.",
      "verse": "16:21",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 304.946,
      "end": 309.265,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, did speak much unto my brethren,",
      "verse": "16:22",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 309.445,
      "end": 312.139,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because they had hardened their hearts again,",
      "verse": "16:22",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 312.319,
      "end": 315.105,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even unto complaining against the Lord their God.",
      "verse": "16:22",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 315.785,
      "end": 320.243,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, did make out of wood a bow,",
      "verse": "16:23",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 320.423,
      "end": 322.977,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and out of a straight stick, an arrow;",
      "verse": "16:23",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 323.157,
      "end": 326.733,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I did arm myself with a bow and an arrow,",
      "verse": "16:23",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 326.913,
      "end": 329.049,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with a sling and with stones.",
      "verse": "16:23",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 329.229,
      "end": 330.947,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said unto my father:",
      "verse": "16:23",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 331.127,
      "end": 333.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Whither shall I go to obtain food?",
      "verse": "16:23",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 334.129,
      "end": 337.008,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that he did inquire of the Lord,",
      "verse": "16:24",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 337.188,
      "end": 340.253,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they had humbled themselves because of my words;",
      "verse": "16:24",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 340.433,
      "end": 344.334,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I did say many things unto them in the energy of my soul.",
      "verse": "16:24",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 345.014,
      "end": 349.286,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the voice of the Lord came unto my father;",
      "verse": "16:25",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 349.466,
      "end": 351.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he was truly chastened",
      "verse": "16:25",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 351.364,
      "end": 353.732,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of his murmuring against the Lord,",
      "verse": "16:25",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 353.912,
      "end": 357.488,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that he was brought down into the depths of sorrow.",
      "verse": "16:25",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 358.168,
      "end": 361.419,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the voice of the Lord said unto him:",
      "verse": "16:26",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 361.599,
      "end": 362.992,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look upon the ball,",
      "verse": "16:26",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 363.172,
      "end": 365.494,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold the things which are written.",
      "verse": "16:26",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 366.174,
      "end": 369.889,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when my father beheld the things",
      "verse": "16:27",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 370.069,
      "end": 372.484,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were written upon the ball,",
      "verse": "16:27",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 372.664,
      "end": 375.265,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he did fear and tremble exceedingly,",
      "verse": "16:27",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 375.445,
      "end": 379.021,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my brethren and the sons of Ishmael and our wives.",
      "verse": "16:27",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 379.701,
      "end": 385.97,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, beheld the pointers which were in the ball,",
      "verse": "16:28",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 386.15,
      "end": 387.636,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they did work",
      "verse": "16:28",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 387.816,
      "end": 392.414,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the faith and diligence and heed which we did give unto them.",
      "verse": "16:28",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 393.094,
      "end": 396.67,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there was also written upon them a new writing,",
      "verse": "16:29",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 396.85,
      "end": 398.661,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was plain to be read,",
      "verse": "16:29",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 398.841,
      "end": 401.349,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which did give us understanding",
      "verse": "16:29",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 401.529,
      "end": 404.687,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the ways of the Lord; and it was written",
      "verse": "16:29",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 404.867,
      "end": 407.189,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and changed from time to time,",
      "verse": "16:29",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 407.369,
      "end": 410.48,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the faith and diligence which we gave unto it.",
      "verse": "16:29",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 410.66,
      "end": 415.676,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus we see that by small means the Lord can bring about great things.",
      "verse": "16:29",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 416.356,
      "end": 421.372,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, did go forth up into the top of the mountain,",
      "verse": "16:30",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 421.552,
      "end": 424.617,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the directions which were given upon the ball.",
      "verse": "16:30",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 425.297,
      "end": 428.408,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I did slay wild beasts,",
      "verse": "16:31",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 428.588,
      "end": 431.653,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that I did obtain food for our families.",
      "verse": "16:31",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 432.333,
      "end": 435.63,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I did return to our tents,",
      "verse": "16:32",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 435.81,
      "end": 438.086,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "bearing the beasts which I had slain;",
      "verse": "16:32",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 438.266,
      "end": 441.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and now when they beheld that I had obtained food,",
      "verse": "16:32",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 441.65,
      "end": 443.461,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "how great was their joy!",
      "verse": "16:32",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 443.641,
      "end": 447.728,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they did humble themselves before the Lord,",
      "verse": "16:32",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 447.908,
      "end": 449.812,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did give thanks unto him.",
      "verse": "16:32",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 450.492,
      "end": 454.207,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we did again take our journey,",
      "verse": "16:33",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 454.387,
      "end": 457.777,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "traveling nearly the same course as in the beginning;",
      "verse": "16:33",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 457.957,
      "end": 460.0,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after we had traveled",
      "verse": "16:33",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 460.18,
      "end": 463.477,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the space of many days we did pitch our tents again,",
      "verse": "16:33",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 463.657,
      "end": 466.397,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we might tarry for the space of a time.",
      "verse": "16:33",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 467.077,
      "end": 469.445,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that Ishmael died,",
      "verse": "16:34",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 469.625,
      "end": 472.644,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and was buried in the place which was called Nahom.",
      "verse": "16:34",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 473.324,
      "end": 477.736,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the daughters of Ishmael did mourn exceedingly,",
      "verse": "16:35",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 477.916,
      "end": 479.913,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the loss of their father,",
      "verse": "16:35",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 480.093,
      "end": 483.622,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and because of their afflictions in the wilderness;",
      "verse": "16:35",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 483.802,
      "end": 486.356,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they did murmur against my father,",
      "verse": "16:35",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 486.536,
      "end": 491.087,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because he had brought them out of the land of Jerusalem, saying:",
      "verse": "16:35",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 491.267,
      "end": 492.846,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Our father is dead;",
      "verse": "16:35",
      "lineIndex": 161
    },
    {
      "start": 493.026,
      "end": 496.323,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and we have wandered much in the wilderness,",
      "verse": "16:35",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 496.503,
      "end": 501.704,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we have suffered much affliction, hunger, thirst, and fatigue;",
      "verse": "16:35",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 501.884,
      "end": 504.02,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after all these sufferings",
      "verse": "16:35",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 504.2,
      "end": 506.801,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we must perish in the wilderness with hunger.",
      "verse": "16:35",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 507.481,
      "end": 509.942,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus they did murmur against my father,",
      "verse": "16:36",
      "lineIndex": 166
    },
    {
      "start": 510.122,
      "end": 511.608,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also against me;",
      "verse": "16:36",
      "lineIndex": 167
    },
    {
      "start": 511.788,
      "end": 514.807,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were desirous to return again to Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "16:36",
      "lineIndex": 168
    },
    {
      "start": 515.487,
      "end": 519.063,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And Laman said unto Lemuel and also unto the sons of Ishmael:",
      "verse": "16:37",
      "lineIndex": 170
    },
    {
      "start": 519.243,
      "end": 521.054,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, let us slay our father",
      "verse": "16:37",
      "lineIndex": 171
    },
    {
      "start": 521.234,
      "end": 523.324,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also our brother Nephi,",
      "verse": "16:37",
      "lineIndex": 172
    },
    {
      "start": 523.504,
      "end": 527.219,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who has taken it upon him to be our ruler and our teacher,",
      "verse": "16:37",
      "lineIndex": 173
    },
    {
      "start": 527.399,
      "end": 529.349,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who are his elder brethren.",
      "verse": "16:37",
      "lineIndex": 174
    },
    {
      "start": 530.029,
      "end": 532.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now, he says that the Lord has talked with him,",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 175
    },
    {
      "start": 532.995,
      "end": 536.014,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also that angels have ministered unto him.",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 176
    },
    {
      "start": 536.194,
      "end": 538.888,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, we know that he lies unto us;",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 177
    },
    {
      "start": 539.068,
      "end": 540.786,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he tells us these things,",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 178
    },
    {
      "start": 540.966,
      "end": 544.077,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he worketh many things by his cunning arts",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 179
    },
    {
      "start": 544.257,
      "end": 546.254,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he may deceive our eyes,",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 180
    },
    {
      "start": 546.434,
      "end": 547.874,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "thinking, perhaps,",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 181
    },
    {
      "start": 548.054,
      "end": 551.816,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he may lead us away into some strange wilderness;",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 182
    },
    {
      "start": 551.996,
      "end": 554.039,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after he has led us away,",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 183
    },
    {
      "start": 554.219,
      "end": 557.841,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he has thought to make himself a king and a ruler over us,",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 184
    },
    {
      "start": 558.021,
      "end": 561.179,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he may do with us according to his will and pleasure.",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 185
    },
    {
      "start": 561.359,
      "end": 562.938,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 186
    },
    {
      "start": 563.118,
      "end": 566.462,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did my brother Laman stir up their hearts to anger.",
      "verse": "16:38",
      "lineIndex": 187
    },
    {
      "start": 567.142,
      "end": 569.975,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Lord was with us,",
      "verse": "16:39",
      "lineIndex": 188
    },
    {
      "start": 570.155,
      "end": 572.756,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even the voice of the Lord came",
      "verse": "16:39",
      "lineIndex": 189
    },
    {
      "start": 572.936,
      "end": 575.583,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did speak many words unto them,",
      "verse": "16:39",
      "lineIndex": 190
    },
    {
      "start": 575.763,
      "end": 578.039,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did chasten them exceedingly;",
      "verse": "16:39",
      "lineIndex": 191
    },
    {
      "start": 578.219,
      "end": 581.191,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after they were chastened by the voice of the Lord",
      "verse": "16:39",
      "lineIndex": 192
    },
    {
      "start": 581.371,
      "end": 583.321,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they did turn away their anger,",
      "verse": "16:39",
      "lineIndex": 193
    },
    {
      "start": 583.501,
      "end": 585.637,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did repent of their sins,",
      "verse": "16:39",
      "lineIndex": 194
    },
    {
      "start": 585.817,
      "end": 589.161,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that the Lord did bless us again with food,",
      "verse": "16:39",
      "lineIndex": 195
    },
    {
      "start": 589.341,
      "end": 590.874,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we did not perish.",
      "verse": "16:39",
      "lineIndex": 196
    }
  ]
}